1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,833
[Witch Baba's jingle plays]

2
00:00:07,916 --> 00:00:12,000
WITCH BABA

3
00:00:12,083 --> 00:00:14,916
[Witch Baba] <i>Last time, I predicted</i>
<i>that someone would fall to their death</i>

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,041
<i>from a bridge.</i>

5
00:00:16,125 --> 00:00:17,583
<i>It really happened, huh?</i>

6
00:00:17,666 --> 00:00:18,750
DIE

7
00:00:19,375 --> 00:00:20,375
[mouse clicking]

8
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:25,083
WITCH BABA

9
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:27,750
[Witch Baba] <i>Is everyone</i>
<i>looking forward to lunch tomorrow?</i>

10
00:00:28,458 --> 00:00:29,291
<i>Is e--</i>

11
00:00:30,541 --> 00:00:31,666
[in reverse] <i>Yo Tzu.</i>

12
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:38,083
<i>Who says one must eat pomelo--</i>
<i>must eat-- festival-- festival--</i>

13
00:00:38,166 --> 00:00:42,041
<i>Who says one must eat pomelo</i>
<i>during Mid-Autumn Festival?</i>

14
00:00:43,541 --> 00:00:45,375
DIE, YO TZU

15
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:48,583
- [key taps]
- [Witch Baba's jingle plays on video]

16
00:00:48,666 --> 00:00:52,125
[glitching SFX playing]

17
00:00:52,208 --> 00:00:55,875
[Witch Baba, distorted] <i>Hello, guys!</i>
<i>Coming up is the prediction for next time.</i>

18
00:00:55,958 --> 00:01:00,583
<i>For tomorrow's KOL STAGE,</i>
<i>Yo Tzu will die.</i>

19
00:01:00,666 --> 00:01:02,375
[cash register SFX playing]

20
00:01:02,458 --> 00:01:05,833
[Witch Baba giggling, distorted]

21
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:17,000
[keys tapping]

22
00:01:17,083 --> 00:01:18,166
[mouse clicks]

23
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:20,291
UTURN MEMBER

24
00:01:20,375 --> 00:01:21,708
YANG CHIH-YUAN, HSU TZU-LU,

25
00:01:21,791 --> 00:01:24,083
CHEN WEN-CHUAN, HUANG HSI-HSI,
YU LING-LING, FANG CHUN-JONG,

26
00:01:24,166 --> 00:01:26,041
LIU HSIAO-LI, LI I-JU,
HSU HUI-CHEN, LI CHUN-SHAN

27
00:01:26,625 --> 00:01:29,125
[opening theme music playing]

28
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,541
[singer singing in Mandarin]

29
00:01:57,041 --> 00:01:59,583
[music ends]

30
00:01:59,666 --> 00:02:03,583
- [crickets chirping]
- [dog barking in distance]

31
00:02:06,791 --> 00:02:09,083
- [A-Hua] Mr. Jen.
- [Mr. Li] Chill. Chill.

32
00:02:10,541 --> 00:02:13,083
I'll go. Take them back to the station.

33
00:02:14,958 --> 00:02:16,250
I'll go with him.

34
00:02:16,333 --> 00:02:17,708
- In the car.
- [Hsin-ping] Ah…

35
00:02:18,208 --> 00:02:19,333
I need to. I must…

36
00:02:19,416 --> 00:02:21,625
You following? You'll mess it up.

37
00:02:22,208 --> 00:02:23,458
It's not your fight.

38
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,541
Get in the car.

39
00:02:25,625 --> 00:02:26,625
Take them.

40
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:28,750
Hurry.

41
00:02:30,875 --> 00:02:31,875
- [Hsin-ping] Come on.
- Go.

42
00:02:39,791 --> 00:02:40,791
[Hsin-ping] Get in.

43
00:02:52,541 --> 00:02:54,500
[sighs]

44
00:02:57,208 --> 00:02:58,583
[exhales]

45
00:03:01,791 --> 00:03:03,708
You really gonna do nothing?

46
00:03:05,208 --> 00:03:06,750
[Hsin-ping] What else can I do?

47
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:14,000
Tomorrow, I'm meant to die.

48
00:03:20,208 --> 00:03:22,125
You're not gonna save me, huh?

49
00:03:24,458 --> 00:03:25,791
[Witch Baba] <i>Hello, guys!</i>

50
00:03:25,875 --> 00:03:27,958
<i>Coming up is the prediction for next time.</i>

51
00:03:28,541 --> 00:03:29,541
<i>- There's no way.</i>
<i>- That's so fake.</i>

52
00:03:29,625 --> 00:03:31,333
<i>- We have to go. It'll be so good.</i>
<i>- I can't believe it.</i>

53
00:03:31,416 --> 00:03:33,416
- [netizen 1] <i>You're kidding.</i>
- [netizen 2] <i>Nah. No way!</i>

54
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:35,875
<i>- Watch carefully. This girl is ruthless.</i>
<i>- Wait. Are you serious?</i>

55
00:03:35,958 --> 00:03:37,666
<i>- Hilarious.</i>
<i>- Police must have given up on Yo Tzu.</i>

56
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,625
<i>- Why does it sound so familiar?</i>
<i>- Do you know what Yo Tzu has done?</i>

57
00:03:39,708 --> 00:03:41,291
<i>- You can do it, Witch Baba!</i>
<i>- You can do it, Yo Tzu.</i>

58
00:03:41,375 --> 00:03:42,875
<i>- Take off the mask!</i>
<i>- Can people stop dying?</i>

59
00:03:42,958 --> 00:03:44,250
[internet café visitor 1]
What are the tickets now?

60
00:03:45,458 --> 00:03:47,541
6,000? Really?

61
00:03:47,625 --> 00:03:48,583
[visitor 2] Up to 10,000!

62
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:50,000
[visitor 3] Half of these are scams.

63
00:03:50,083 --> 00:03:52,708
[visitor 1] It's over 30,000
for a ticket now!

64
00:03:52,791 --> 00:03:54,208
OCTOBER 6TH

65
00:03:54,291 --> 00:03:56,875
[crowd cheering]

66
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:20,375
[fan 1] Yo Tzu is so cool.

67
00:04:21,375 --> 00:04:22,750
[fan 2] Yeah. He's awesome.

68
00:04:24,583 --> 00:04:27,125
[staff] Just keep moving,
please. Thank you. Oh.

69
00:04:27,208 --> 00:04:30,541
Just keep moving. Thank you.
Yes. Keep moving. Yes. Yes, thank you.

70
00:04:30,625 --> 00:04:32,833
[police siren wails]

71
00:04:32,916 --> 00:04:36,166
TAIPEI CITY FIRST PRECINCT

72
00:04:36,250 --> 00:04:37,458
- [fan 3] Oh, is that Yo Tzu?
- [fan 4] Yo Tzu!

73
00:04:37,541 --> 00:04:39,041
- [fan 5] Yo Tzu!
- [fans squealing]

74
00:04:39,125 --> 00:04:43,791
[fans cheering]

75
00:04:43,875 --> 00:04:45,708
- [fan 6] Yo Tzu!
- [fan 7] Yo Tzu!

76
00:04:56,875 --> 00:04:58,666
[officer 1] You. Take the mask off.

77
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:02,500
Hey, you! Freeze!

78
00:05:04,583 --> 00:05:05,583
You good?

79
00:05:07,625 --> 00:05:09,208
Why are you wearing a mask?

80
00:05:09,291 --> 00:05:11,333
[masked fan] Someone's
giving them out at the station.

81
00:05:12,916 --> 00:05:14,833
[staff] Please scan
your code here. Thank you.

82
00:05:14,916 --> 00:05:15,916
Yes. Thank you.

83
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,166
Yes. Yes, you-- Yep. You can take that in.

84
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:19,916
- [fan 8] How much?
- [staff] Thank you.

85
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,375
Please move over here, please. This way.

86
00:05:25,583 --> 00:05:26,750
[Chia-jen] Kuo Ta-fu!

87
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,750
Move aside.

88
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,375
- [fan 9] Hey.
- [fan 10] Hey.

89
00:05:36,458 --> 00:05:38,708
- [fan 11] Dude. Stop pushing.
- [fan 12] Hey! Watch it.

90
00:05:39,208 --> 00:05:40,208
[Chia-jen] Out of the way.

91
00:05:40,291 --> 00:05:41,333
- [fan 13] Hey.
- [fan 14] Excuse me.

92
00:05:41,416 --> 00:05:42,666
[fan 15] Hey! Yo!

93
00:05:43,291 --> 00:05:44,541
[fan 16] Excuse me.

94
00:05:44,625 --> 00:05:47,250
- [fan 17] Hey! What the…
- [Chia-jen] Hey! Stop him! Stop him now!

95
00:05:47,333 --> 00:05:50,166
- [fan 18] It's the guy from the video.
- [Chia-jen] Stop him! Block all of them!

96
00:05:51,625 --> 00:05:53,875
[Chen-wei] Chia-jen.
The venue's already surrounded.

97
00:05:53,958 --> 00:05:56,250
People can come in, but not go out.

98
00:05:56,333 --> 00:05:57,666
[fan 19] Hey. It's about to start.

99
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,083
Your men are ready.

100
00:06:01,375 --> 00:06:02,833
What do you think about my makeup?

101
00:06:02,916 --> 00:06:04,458
- [Wan-wan] You look so good.
- [giggles]

102
00:06:04,541 --> 00:06:05,916
[Wan-wan] Hey, did you see
the video from yesterday?

103
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,208
[Little Egg] Yeah. It was terrifying.

104
00:06:07,291 --> 00:06:08,916
[Wan-wan] But you have to admit
she's the content queen right now.

105
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,416
- [Little Egg] Yeah. It's pretty true.
- [Wan-wan] Yeah.

106
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:12,041
Recently, I've been thinking
about it so much.

107
00:06:12,125 --> 00:06:15,333
Hey, bro. Do you think Yo Tzu will come?

108
00:06:15,416 --> 00:06:17,000
- Nah.
- Yeah. I think he'll come. Surely.

109
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:18,583
Well, who knows?

110
00:06:19,458 --> 00:06:22,458
- [Braised Egg] There's no way he comes.
- [Hippo] Hey. He has a fan meeting today.

111
00:06:24,666 --> 00:06:26,416
Huh? Who's this?

112
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,500
Yo, yo.

113
00:06:27,583 --> 00:06:30,500
[fans chattering, indistinct]

114
00:06:58,041 --> 00:07:04,583
[fans cheering, chattering, indistinct]

115
00:07:14,375 --> 00:07:19,125
[fans chanting] Yo Tzu!

116
00:07:19,208 --> 00:07:22,666
[cheering]

117
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,833
[microphone feedback sound]

118
00:07:23,916 --> 00:07:28,041
[energetic music playing on speakers]

119
00:07:29,375 --> 00:07:31,500
What's going on? It's not time yet, right?

120
00:07:31,583 --> 00:07:34,083
[staff 1] I-I've lost control
of the main broadcast.

121
00:07:34,166 --> 00:07:36,125
Someone's taken remote access.

122
00:07:37,958 --> 00:07:40,666
- [energetic music stops]
- [Witch Baba's jingle plays on speakers]

123
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:41,666
[glitching SFX plays]

124
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,791
WITCH BABA

125
00:07:43,875 --> 00:07:46,166
[fans cheering]

126
00:07:48,291 --> 00:07:50,875
[Witch Baba, distorted]
<i>Welcome to KOL STAGE.</i>

127
00:07:50,958 --> 00:07:52,541
<i>I'm Witch Baba.</i>

128
00:07:55,833 --> 00:07:57,375
Can you check the source of the signal?

129
00:07:57,458 --> 00:07:58,958
[officer 2] The network's been cut off.

130
00:07:59,041 --> 00:08:01,416
Someone's established
a direct connection to the screen.

131
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,000
That means he's here.

132
00:08:03,083 --> 00:08:05,458
[Witch Baba] <i>Thank you</i>
<i>for still coming to support influencers</i>

133
00:08:05,541 --> 00:08:06,916
<i>at a time like this.</i>

134
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:10,041
<i>Even though four influencers</i>
<i>killed two people recently.</i>

135
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:12,083
<i>But you all came anyway.</i>

136
00:08:12,166 --> 00:08:14,541
<i>You're all such brainless fans!</i>

137
00:08:14,625 --> 00:08:17,000
[laughs, distorted]

138
00:08:17,583 --> 00:08:18,875
[elevator dings]

139
00:08:22,375 --> 00:08:24,250
- [officer 3] No pushing. Hey! Make way.
- [Chia-jen] Out of the way.

140
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:26,416
- Make way! Officer coming through.
- [Chia-jen] Get out of the way!

141
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:29,625
[officer 3] Hey. Stop pushing. Hey.
Let him through! Let him through!

142
00:08:31,458 --> 00:08:33,208
- [Chia-jen] Move!
- [Witch Baba] <i>But don't worry.</i>

143
00:08:33,291 --> 00:08:35,750
<i>I killed those four scumbags.</i>

144
00:08:35,833 --> 00:08:37,125
<i>One drowned.</i>

145
00:08:37,208 --> 00:08:39,000
<i>One fell to his death.</i>

146
00:08:39,083 --> 00:08:42,416
<i>One is still in critical condition</i>
<i>at the hospital.</i>

147
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:46,375
<i>Oh yeah. And the other one</i>
<i>will die very soon.</i>

148
00:08:50,291 --> 00:08:53,708
<i>So, you all came to see Yo Tzu die, right?</i>

149
00:08:53,791 --> 00:08:57,166
<i>Anyway. None of you are to blame, right?</i>

150
00:08:57,250 --> 00:09:01,916
<i>All you did was hide behind a keyboard</i>
<i>and type. You just liked a post.</i>

151
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:05,166
[laughs] <i>This is hilarious.</i>

152
00:09:05,250 --> 00:09:06,791
<i>You're all so brainless.</i>

153
00:09:06,875 --> 00:09:09,041
[fan 1] What the hell?
There's no way she's talking about us.

154
00:09:09,125 --> 00:09:11,083
[fan 2] Shut up! You're the brainless one.

155
00:09:12,916 --> 00:09:15,000
[Witch Baba] <i>So brainless.</i>

156
00:09:15,083 --> 00:09:19,083
<i>Brainless fans raise brainless influencers</i>

157
00:09:19,166 --> 00:09:22,875
<i>and create this brainless internet world.</i>

158
00:09:22,958 --> 00:09:24,583
<i>So good.</i>

159
00:09:24,666 --> 00:09:29,791
<i>Stop hiding behind the keyboard.</i>
<i>Let people see what you guys look like.</i>

160
00:09:29,875 --> 00:09:33,458
<i>- Yay! All of you should go to hell.</i>
- [pop-ups chiming]

161
00:09:33,541 --> 00:09:35,916
- [Witch Baba laughing]
- [cash register SFX playing]

162
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,791
[fan 3] What the hell? Can she do that?

163
00:09:37,875 --> 00:09:39,333
[fan 4] Who is she?!

164
00:09:39,416 --> 00:09:41,458
- Come out here and say that!
- [fan 5] Should we call the police?

165
00:09:41,541 --> 00:09:44,250
Turn it off now! Shut it down!

166
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:46,833
[staff 1] I-I can't do anything
from here! I've been shut out.

167
00:09:46,916 --> 00:09:49,125
[pop-ups chiming]

168
00:09:49,208 --> 00:09:50,208
[chiming stops]

169
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:53,541
The killer's in here.
We have to find him now.

170
00:09:53,625 --> 00:09:55,083
[fan 6] Show yourself!

171
00:09:56,041 --> 00:09:58,000
[fan 7] Boo!

172
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:00,833
[fans clamoring]

173
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:02,875
Shit. What the hell?

174
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:04,916
The hell?

175
00:10:05,666 --> 00:10:07,750
Has she gone crazy? What do we even do?

176
00:10:07,833 --> 00:10:09,958
- It'll cause a riot.
- How do we handle this?

177
00:10:10,041 --> 00:10:11,041
[Braised Egg] She's so stupid.

178
00:10:11,125 --> 00:10:12,666
- Did you all see it?
- [Hippo] See what?

179
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,208
- Ah, ah, ah, ah! Yo Tzu!
- [Hippo] Wait. Was that him?

180
00:10:14,291 --> 00:10:15,375
- What…
- Yo. Huh?

181
00:10:15,458 --> 00:10:16,875
- He went that way?
- [Hippo] I think that was him.

182
00:10:16,958 --> 00:10:18,458
- Hey! Wait!
- [A-Hua] Did he take the elevator?

183
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:19,541
[Little Egg] Go after him!

184
00:10:19,625 --> 00:10:21,000
[Hippo groans] I was first.

185
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:23,291
- Hey, fat-ass. Get out of the way.
- You're blocking the whole door.

186
00:10:23,375 --> 00:10:25,166
REGULAR MEMBER - PREMIUM MEMBER

187
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,583
[fan 8] Screw you, bitch.

188
00:10:26,666 --> 00:10:29,958
[fan 9] You suck!
Stop hiding and come out here!

189
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:36,583
[Yo Tzu] Hello.

190
00:10:40,333 --> 00:10:42,083
That's not the real Witch Baba.

191
00:10:43,125 --> 00:10:45,416
- Yo Tzu!
- [fan 10] Yo Tzu, wait! Don't!

192
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,958
- [fan 11] How dare you say that?
- [fan 12] Who are you to say that?

193
00:10:48,041 --> 00:10:49,916
Yo Tzu!

194
00:10:52,333 --> 00:10:54,333
[staff 2] Hey, wha… what do we do?
Sh… Should I plug it back in?

195
00:10:54,416 --> 00:10:55,875
Move fast!

196
00:11:00,041 --> 00:11:01,250
[microphone feedback sound]

197
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,916
[fan 13] Shut up!

198
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:07,000
- [fan 14] This is your fault!
- Anyway, I'm probably gonna die today.

199
00:11:07,083 --> 00:11:09,083
- [fan 15] What are you talking about?
- [fan 16] Go to hell!

200
00:11:09,166 --> 00:11:11,583
But I need to say something before I do.

201
00:11:11,666 --> 00:11:16,375
[fans clamoring]

202
00:11:16,458 --> 00:11:18,625
This whole thing started because…

203
00:11:20,791 --> 00:11:21,625
[fan 17] Murderer!

204
00:11:21,708 --> 00:11:23,333
[fan 18] What the hell
is this guy talking about?

205
00:11:23,416 --> 00:11:27,833
…because a year ago, Wei Yen, Wa Zai,
Kao Pi, and I caused a car accident.

206
00:11:27,916 --> 00:11:29,166
[fan 19] Fuck off, dumbass!

207
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:32,333
[Yo Tzu] We really didn't think
it was that serious at the time.

208
00:11:33,125 --> 00:11:34,250
But it's still on us.

209
00:11:34,333 --> 00:11:37,041
- [fan 20] As if you can talk!
- [fan 21] How can you say that?!

210
00:11:37,125 --> 00:11:39,250
And, because of us, someone died.

211
00:11:41,250 --> 00:11:42,583
To the victim,

212
00:11:43,833 --> 00:11:45,500
to their family…

213
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:47,458
[Wan-wan] What is actually
going on right now?

214
00:11:47,541 --> 00:11:49,291
- [Chih-chiang] I did not expect this.
- I'm so confused.

215
00:11:49,375 --> 00:11:51,291
- [A-Hua] What's happening?
- Why did he come?

216
00:11:51,375 --> 00:11:52,583
- [A-Hua] What's the situation?
- So cool.

217
00:11:53,333 --> 00:11:54,333
…I apologize.

218
00:11:54,416 --> 00:11:56,333
[fan 22] You're too late, bro!

219
00:11:56,416 --> 00:11:57,875
[fans] Boo!

220
00:11:57,958 --> 00:12:00,333
- What I did was wrong, and I'm sorry.
- [fan clamoring]

221
00:12:00,416 --> 00:12:01,416
[fan 23] Get down.

222
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,250
- [fan 24] Get off the stage!
- [fan 25] Get off the stage!

223
00:12:03,333 --> 00:12:05,416
[fan 26] Get off the stage.

224
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:06,416
[fan 27] Boo!

225
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:09,083
[fans chanting] Get off!

226
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:10,166
Oh, that was so manly.

227
00:12:10,250 --> 00:12:12,416
- Is this okay? Are you guys sure?
- [Braised Egg] Cool! Yes! This is dope.

228
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,916
Did the police ask him to say this?

229
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:17,916
[Yo Tzu] From now on,
I'll cooperate with the police.

230
00:12:19,791 --> 00:12:21,625
And accept full responsibility.

231
00:12:22,916 --> 00:12:26,375
So please listen to me.
Listen to what I have to say.

232
00:12:26,458 --> 00:12:28,500
[fan 28] You suck! Get off the stage!

233
00:12:28,583 --> 00:12:31,000
- [fans] Boo!
- [fan 29] Get off the stage!

234
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:34,208
[Yo Tzu] These murders
have nothing to do with Witch Baba.

235
00:12:34,291 --> 00:12:35,333
Yo Tzu!

236
00:12:35,416 --> 00:12:37,375
She is also a victim.

237
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,208
- The real killer…
- Get down!

238
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,208
…wanted to get revenge.

239
00:12:44,291 --> 00:12:46,083
[fan 30] You suck! Boo!

240
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:48,958
- And blame it on influencers.
- [fan 31] Get off the stage!

241
00:12:49,041 --> 00:12:50,833
[Yo Tzu] So, he kidnapped
Witch Baba's friend…

242
00:12:50,916 --> 00:12:52,250
[fan 32] What is he talking about?

243
00:12:52,333 --> 00:12:54,750
…and forced her to make prediction videos.

244
00:12:55,333 --> 00:12:58,833
He's already kept Witch Baba's friend
hostage for over a week.

245
00:12:58,916 --> 00:12:59,916
[fan 33] Who?

246
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,500
[fan 34] Who? Who is it?

247
00:13:01,583 --> 00:13:02,583
[fan 35] Who?

248
00:13:04,083 --> 00:13:06,333
[Yo Tzu] So I wanna
tell the killer, right now…

249
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:07,875
- [fan 36] Yeah, if you got the balls!
- [fan 37] What do you want to say?

250
00:13:07,958 --> 00:13:09,500
- [fan 38] Let him speak!
- [Yo Tzu] I'm sorry.

251
00:13:09,583 --> 00:13:12,458
[clamoring stops]

252
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:14,125
I hurt your family.

253
00:13:14,208 --> 00:13:16,416
- [fans] Boo!
- [fan 39] It's too late! It's useless now.

254
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,500
[fan 40] You suck!

255
00:13:17,583 --> 00:13:19,791
[Yo Tzu] But the person
you kidnapped is innocent.

256
00:13:20,875 --> 00:13:22,375
What you did is wrong.

257
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:25,791
If you're really seeking justice…

258
00:13:28,791 --> 00:13:30,375
Come on! Come and get me now!

259
00:13:30,958 --> 00:13:32,541
[fans clamoring]

260
00:13:34,875 --> 00:13:37,458
- [Yo Tzu] You know where to find me.
- Get down, Yo Tzu!

261
00:13:38,833 --> 00:13:41,333
[Yo Tzu] Right here!

262
00:13:45,083 --> 00:13:46,791
Come on. Come get me.

263
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,208
[fan 41] Do it first!

264
00:13:53,708 --> 00:13:55,083
[fan 42] How can you talk?

265
00:14:00,125 --> 00:14:02,208
[Yo Tzu] Baba and I are waiting for you.

266
00:14:08,958 --> 00:14:10,166
We're right here!

267
00:14:11,208 --> 00:14:13,583
We're waiting for you right here.

268
00:14:19,041 --> 00:14:20,125
Hey. What are you doing?

269
00:14:20,208 --> 00:14:23,166
[Wan-wan] Why would he do that?
Like, actually, why?

270
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:25,333
- Hey, Yo Tzu, where are you going?
- [Little Egg] Yo Tzu!

271
00:14:25,416 --> 00:14:26,500
- [A-Hua] Hey! Hey!
- [Hippo] Yo Tzu.

272
00:14:26,583 --> 00:14:28,708
- Where are you going?
- What's going on? Are you guys…

273
00:14:28,791 --> 00:14:30,125
[A-Hua] Get out of the way!

274
00:14:30,208 --> 00:14:31,208
[grunts]

275
00:14:32,833 --> 00:14:33,833
[door closes]

276
00:14:34,666 --> 00:14:37,916
[A-Hua grunting]

277
00:14:44,041 --> 00:14:45,250
- [blow lands]
- What are you doing?

278
00:14:45,333 --> 00:14:46,333
[blade clinks]

279
00:14:49,041 --> 00:14:50,208
[blade slashes]

280
00:14:52,125 --> 00:14:53,333
[Yo Tzu groans]

281
00:14:57,875 --> 00:14:59,833
[both grunting]

282
00:15:11,791 --> 00:15:15,250
[both grunting]

283
00:15:25,125 --> 00:15:26,375
- [blade slashes]
- [Yo Tzu groans]

284
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:30,166
- [blood squelching]
- [Ta-fu grunting]

285
00:15:30,250 --> 00:15:34,041
[Yo Tzu groaning, breathing shakily]

286
00:15:35,041 --> 00:15:36,041
[blade clinks]

287
00:15:38,541 --> 00:15:41,166
[Ta-fu] Who gave you the right
to say that nonsense?

288
00:15:42,208 --> 00:15:44,875
Who gave you the right to say that?!

289
00:15:49,333 --> 00:15:50,625
[Yo Tzu] You did.

290
00:15:50,708 --> 00:15:52,250
[Ta-fu grunting]

291
00:15:57,708 --> 00:15:59,291
Yo Tzu, run.

292
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,000
Go! Get out of here!

293
00:16:01,083 --> 00:16:02,791
[both grunting]

294
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:07,833
[Hsin-ping panting]

295
00:16:12,125 --> 00:16:14,166
[both grunting]

296
00:16:16,666 --> 00:16:17,833
[handgun clicks]

297
00:16:25,333 --> 00:16:26,875
[fans clamoring]

298
00:16:27,708 --> 00:16:28,750
[Chia-jen] Police!

299
00:16:32,958 --> 00:16:34,500
[Wan-wan] Guys, is this serious?

300
00:16:34,583 --> 00:16:36,833
- [Little Egg] Oh my God. What's going on?
- Hey! Where's Yo Tzu?

301
00:16:36,916 --> 00:16:38,541
- That way.
- Through that door.

302
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,125
[Ta-fu] Go on. Shoot.

303
00:16:59,541 --> 00:17:01,666
[Hsin-ping] Hey? Hey.

304
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:03,791
[gasps] Oh my God.

305
00:17:05,958 --> 00:17:08,083
Yo Tzu? Can you get up?

306
00:17:08,166 --> 00:17:09,791
Come on. Let's go. [grunts]

307
00:17:09,875 --> 00:17:13,333
[A-Hua] And the door's locked now.
I can't go after them. They went down.

308
00:17:13,416 --> 00:17:17,041
Hey. Is there anyone
we can notify downstairs at the back?

309
00:17:18,541 --> 00:17:19,791
Yes. Block 'em.

310
00:17:19,875 --> 00:17:22,666
[fans shouting, indistinct]

311
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:29,375
[police sirens wailing in distance]

312
00:17:54,333 --> 00:17:55,458
[Chia-jen] Kuo Ta-fu!

313
00:17:59,416 --> 00:18:00,666
[Ta-fu] Fuck.

314
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:03,166
[engine starts]

315
00:18:03,250 --> 00:18:04,250
[Chia-jen] Get out!

316
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:10,916
[Chia-jen grunting]

317
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,791
[tires squealing]

318
00:18:24,375 --> 00:18:25,500
[Chia-jen] Stop the car!

319
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:27,750
- Stop!
- [handgun clicking]

320
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,000
[tires squeal]

321
00:18:30,083 --> 00:18:32,625
- [Chia-jen grunting]
- [handgun drops]

322
00:18:32,708 --> 00:18:35,000
[tires squealing]

323
00:18:36,125 --> 00:18:37,291
[Chia-jen groaning]

324
00:18:39,833 --> 00:18:42,708
[Yu-chieh's music track playing on video]

325
00:18:42,791 --> 00:18:48,291
[Yu-chieh] ♪ <i>What's lost is lost… </i>♪

326
00:18:50,333 --> 00:18:51,458
[Chia-jen grunting]

327
00:18:51,541 --> 00:18:55,875
- [Yu-chieh on video] ♪ <i>hold Nothing… </i>♪
- [Chia-jen inhales sharply, groans]

328
00:19:00,958 --> 00:19:02,916
[both grunting]

329
00:19:11,625 --> 00:19:14,250
[Ta-fu groaning]

330
00:19:14,833 --> 00:19:15,875
[Chia-jen groans]

331
00:19:16,916 --> 00:19:19,208
Where's my daughter?! Where is she?!

332
00:19:19,291 --> 00:19:21,958
- [blade slashes]
- [Chia-jen groaning]

333
00:19:22,041 --> 00:19:23,666
Tell me where she is.

334
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,958
- My daughter!
- [punches landing]

335
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,125
[Chia-jen] Where is she?!

336
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:35,416
[Ta-fu] She's dead.

337
00:19:36,666 --> 00:19:38,666
- [punches landing]
- [both grunting]

338
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:42,333
- [Chia-jen] Where is she?!
- [Ta-fu] She's dead!

339
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:10,958
[Chia-jen groaning]

340
00:20:12,541 --> 00:20:15,333
<i>This next song is for my dad.</i>

341
00:20:15,875 --> 00:20:18,625
<i>He didn't come today. Lucky for me.</i>

342
00:20:20,916 --> 00:20:22,291
<i>My dad's a cop.</i>

343
00:20:25,833 --> 00:20:27,750
<i>He's a pretty boring old man.</i>

344
00:20:31,416 --> 00:20:35,208
<i>To him, the internet</i>
<i>is only used to send boomer memes.</i>

345
00:20:35,291 --> 00:20:38,416
<i>That's why he's really against</i>
<i>me becoming an influencer.</i>

346
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:41,291
<i>And why he doesn't want</i>
<i>me to be a singer either.</i>

347
00:20:42,083 --> 00:20:43,166
[blade clinks]

348
00:20:43,916 --> 00:20:45,250
[Chia-jen groans]

349
00:20:45,333 --> 00:20:48,375
[Yu-chieh] <i>He always asks me,</i>
<i>"Why are you doing live streams?"</i>

350
00:20:48,458 --> 00:20:50,583
<i>"Is the internet that fun?"</i>

351
00:20:50,666 --> 00:20:52,166
<i>Well, yeah. It's pretty fun.</i>

352
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:55,041
[audience laughs]

353
00:20:55,791 --> 00:20:59,541
The last time I saw him,
we had a big argument.

354
00:21:00,708 --> 00:21:03,000
I ended up reporting him to the police.

355
00:21:03,083 --> 00:21:06,166
[audience laughs]

356
00:21:07,166 --> 00:21:09,625
I haven't seen him in a year.

357
00:21:10,708 --> 00:21:13,666
I thought I wanted him out of my life.

358
00:21:15,083 --> 00:21:17,833
But now I kind of wish he was here.

359
00:21:19,375 --> 00:21:20,458
I wanna tell him…

360
00:21:20,541 --> 00:21:23,250
- [Hippo] Inhale, exhale.
- [Little Egg] It's okay. Breathe in…

361
00:21:23,333 --> 00:21:24,333
[Braised Egg] Chill.

362
00:21:24,416 --> 00:21:26,416
[Yu-chieh] …that there's still
lots of beauty in this world.

363
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:29,500
- [Hippo] Inhale, exhale. Relax, relax.
- [Little Egg] It's okay. Breathe in…

364
00:21:29,583 --> 00:21:31,250
- [Braised Egg] Calm!
- [Hippo] Inhale, exhale.

365
00:21:31,333 --> 00:21:33,958
[Yu-chieh] Having friends and family
around you when you're down…

366
00:21:34,041 --> 00:21:35,375
[Hsin-ping] I need backup now.

367
00:21:35,458 --> 00:21:39,291
…knowing you're not alone,
makes you feel warm.

368
00:21:39,375 --> 00:21:41,666
[officer] Requesting backup
and med unit, immediately.

369
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,708
[Hsin-ping] Yo Tzu? Don't die on me.

370
00:21:43,791 --> 00:21:45,625
[Yo Tzu chuckles, coughs]

371
00:21:45,708 --> 00:21:48,708
- [footsteps running, receding]
- [Yo Tzu breathing shakily]

372
00:21:48,791 --> 00:21:50,958
[Yu-chieh] And suddenly,
you feel like crying.

373
00:21:51,625 --> 00:21:52,833
You want a hug.

374
00:21:52,916 --> 00:21:54,875
[both grunting]

375
00:21:56,916 --> 00:21:59,166
I wanna hug my daughter too!

376
00:22:04,666 --> 00:22:06,625
[Chia-jen grunting]

377
00:22:14,791 --> 00:22:15,875
- [gunshot]
- [bullet hits]

378
00:22:47,375 --> 00:22:50,583
[Yu-chieh] Dad, I'm doing well.

379
00:22:54,583 --> 00:22:56,875
I finally found my purpose.

380
00:22:59,625 --> 00:23:00,958
And I'm happy.

381
00:23:03,583 --> 00:23:06,875
Someday, if I lose my way…

382
00:23:09,291 --> 00:23:12,083
or find myself in a dark place…

383
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,333
please find me.

384
00:24:28,125 --> 00:24:29,125
[knock on door]

385
00:24:31,250 --> 00:24:32,416
Come in.

386
00:24:34,375 --> 00:24:35,625
How are you?

387
00:24:37,083 --> 00:24:39,333
Li Ting-en!

388
00:24:39,875 --> 00:24:41,250
- Can I hug you?
- Oh!

389
00:24:41,333 --> 00:24:42,750
- You sure?
- Yeah. Please.

390
00:24:42,833 --> 00:24:44,708
- [Ting-en] Mmm!
- I missed you.

391
00:24:44,791 --> 00:24:46,333
[Ting-en] I'm so sorry.

392
00:24:46,416 --> 00:24:48,166
Why are you sorry?

393
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:50,333
I should've found you earlier.

394
00:24:51,291 --> 00:24:52,958
You're not Witch Baba.

395
00:24:53,041 --> 00:24:54,458
- Hey.
- Ah…

396
00:24:54,541 --> 00:24:56,833
- Why would you even say that?
- Ow!

397
00:24:56,916 --> 00:24:58,625
- Owie.
- What's wrong?

398
00:24:58,708 --> 00:25:00,375
You're fine.

399
00:25:00,458 --> 00:25:01,583
[Yu-chieh chuckles]

400
00:25:02,708 --> 00:25:04,500
Did that guy do anything?

401
00:25:05,625 --> 00:25:06,833
Not really.

402
00:25:07,625 --> 00:25:10,208
Just threatened me and tied me up.

403
00:25:10,291 --> 00:25:12,250
He seemed to regret it.

404
00:25:12,333 --> 00:25:13,958
- [Ting-en] That's weird.
- Mmm.

405
00:25:14,041 --> 00:25:15,250
[Ting-en] Do you know why?

406
00:25:17,291 --> 00:25:19,083
Maybe 'cause he…

407
00:25:20,625 --> 00:25:22,916
he had a daughter also.

408
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,791
Maybe when he looked at me,
he thought of her.

409
00:25:27,375 --> 00:25:28,958
That's kind of weird.

410
00:25:33,958 --> 00:25:36,333
- You want some?
- I'm good. [chuckles]

411
00:25:38,083 --> 00:25:41,375
How is your dad? Things okay?

412
00:25:42,333 --> 00:25:45,208
Not sure. I've barely seen him.

413
00:25:45,708 --> 00:25:48,041
He's always in a hurry with work lately.

414
00:25:48,125 --> 00:25:50,583
Mmm. True.
Maybe he just needs some time.

415
00:25:51,250 --> 00:25:55,583
Mmm. Don't know. But I'm not sure
if I'm ready to talk to him.

416
00:25:57,791 --> 00:25:58,791
[Ting-en] Hmm.

417
00:26:00,208 --> 00:26:01,208
Hey.

418
00:26:01,875 --> 00:26:03,666
I spoke to him.

419
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:06,375
- What did you say?
- That you don't know what to say.

420
00:26:06,458 --> 00:26:08,375
Mmm! Blabbermouth!

421
00:26:08,458 --> 00:26:11,708
It's fine. He wishes
that you would go home.

422
00:26:12,958 --> 00:26:13,958
And then?

423
00:26:14,541 --> 00:26:19,125
He said… He said
that he wants you to be free and happy,

424
00:26:19,208 --> 00:26:21,958
but as a dad,
he worries about his daughter.

425
00:26:23,083 --> 00:26:27,166
He worries if you are eating well,
and sleeping well,

426
00:26:27,250 --> 00:26:29,375
and if anyone is bullying you.

427
00:26:31,041 --> 00:26:32,833
There's no way he actually said that.

428
00:26:33,583 --> 00:26:36,541
- He did.
- Yeah, right.

429
00:26:37,041 --> 00:26:38,541
Hey. Actually, he cried.

430
00:26:38,625 --> 00:26:41,291
Okay. Make it more obvious.

431
00:26:41,375 --> 00:26:43,958
- Why are you smiling?
- I'm not!

432
00:26:44,041 --> 00:26:46,166
[officer in distance]
Hello, sir. Still on the job?

433
00:26:46,250 --> 00:26:47,500
Wait. Isn't that your dad?

434
00:26:47,583 --> 00:26:49,166
[footsteps approaching]

435
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,166
- You good?
- [officer] Yes, sir.

436
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:55,416
- Hey! This is your fault!
- [Ting-en] Okay. I'll leave you to it.

437
00:26:55,500 --> 00:26:57,375
- Wait! You can't leave!
- Bye!

438
00:26:57,958 --> 00:27:00,000
- [Yu-chieh] Wait! Come back!
- You should talk to him.

439
00:27:00,083 --> 00:27:01,291
- [Yu-chieh groans]
- Bye!

440
00:27:01,375 --> 00:27:02,375
[door opens]

441
00:27:08,333 --> 00:27:10,166
- Hi.
- [Ting-en] Oh. Mr. Jen.

442
00:27:10,791 --> 00:27:13,166
- [Chia-jen] She awake?
- I'm not sure.

443
00:27:14,625 --> 00:27:15,625
Okay.

444
00:27:16,541 --> 00:27:18,083
I'm leaving. Bye-bye.

445
00:27:23,666 --> 00:27:24,666
[Chia-jen knocks]

446
00:27:55,208 --> 00:27:59,666
[sighs]

447
00:28:29,166 --> 00:28:34,916
[Yu-chieh on video] ♪ <i>And in this moment </i>♪

448
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:37,708
[Yu-chieh's music track playing]

449
00:28:37,791 --> 00:28:43,583
♪ <i>Can you hear my voice? </i>♪

450
00:28:49,125 --> 00:28:51,208
Do you like my singing?

451
00:28:51,291 --> 00:28:54,083
[music continues]

452
00:28:54,166 --> 00:28:55,916
Is it too loud?

453
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,083
[music stops]

454
00:28:57,166 --> 00:28:58,625
Guess what I placed?

455
00:29:02,708 --> 00:29:04,041
First place.

456
00:29:05,041 --> 00:29:06,041
[Yu-chieh chuckles]

457
00:29:12,625 --> 00:29:13,625
Come here.

458
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,000
Hurry up.

459
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:33,916
I'm fine, I'm eating every day,
and no one bullies me.

460
00:29:34,708 --> 00:29:37,125
And if they did, I know you would save me.

461
00:29:40,583 --> 00:29:42,666
And Mom would know that too.

462
00:29:43,541 --> 00:29:44,541
[Chia-jen] Mmm.

463
00:29:45,958 --> 00:29:49,625
[sighs]

464
00:29:49,708 --> 00:29:52,708
[Yu-chieh] Next time,
don't randomly break things, okay?

465
00:29:52,791 --> 00:29:54,000
[Chia-jen, choking] Mmm.

466
00:29:56,541 --> 00:29:58,458
You're not mad anymore?

467
00:29:58,541 --> 00:29:59,791
[Yu-chieh] I'm not.

468
00:30:04,291 --> 00:30:09,333
[Chia-jen sighs, breathing shakily]

469
00:30:09,416 --> 00:30:10,500
[Yu-chieh] Thank you.

470
00:30:38,083 --> 00:30:39,958
[Yo Tzu] When are you gonna wake up, bro?

471
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,166
All our friends are dead.

472
00:30:51,458 --> 00:30:53,125
We killed people.

473
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,333
An innocent mom and daughter.

474
00:31:05,291 --> 00:31:07,125
Why are you still sleeping?

475
00:31:25,916 --> 00:31:27,791
Kao Pi's dad doesn't know.

476
00:31:33,208 --> 00:31:35,750
Wa Zai's mom
doesn't dare tell his grandma.

477
00:31:40,625 --> 00:31:42,250
What am I meant to do, bro?

478
00:31:50,458 --> 00:31:52,708
[sighing]

479
00:32:03,125 --> 00:32:04,708
It's just me and you.

480
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,666
[no audible dialogue]

481
00:32:15,916 --> 00:32:18,625
Don't you wanna have a million followers?

482
00:32:25,791 --> 00:32:28,750
Didn't you say you'll get a house for us?

483
00:32:33,125 --> 00:32:35,208
[sighing]

484
00:32:53,875 --> 00:32:59,041
[rhythmic beeping]

485
00:32:59,125 --> 00:33:03,000
[Ta-fu sighing]

486
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,666
[door opens]

487
00:33:22,208 --> 00:33:23,208
[door closes]

488
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,833
This is what I found on your computer.

489
00:33:29,416 --> 00:33:30,583
[Ta-fu on video] <i>Are you okay?</i>

490
00:33:32,083 --> 00:33:33,666
[Lily] <i>I'm fine. I'll be fine.</i>

491
00:33:35,458 --> 00:33:37,750
<i>Hey, just let them go. Don't get involved.</i>

492
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:40,666
This is the version circulating online.

493
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:43,666
I think Yo Tzu deleted the original.

494
00:33:43,750 --> 00:33:44,958
So, why do you have it?

495
00:33:45,041 --> 00:33:48,833
[influencers chattering,
cheering, laughing on video]

496
00:33:48,916 --> 00:33:50,416
[Hsin-ping] Where did you get it from?

497
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:52,541
[chattering continues, indistinct]

498
00:33:53,041 --> 00:33:54,041
Hey.

499
00:34:06,875 --> 00:34:07,875
[video stops]

500
00:34:09,958 --> 00:34:13,000
There should only be
one version in existence.

501
00:34:13,083 --> 00:34:14,833
Who gave you the other one?

502
00:34:18,625 --> 00:34:22,625
Kuo Ta-fu, you've already
caused two deaths.

503
00:34:22,708 --> 00:34:25,541
You realize you could serve
two life terms for this.

504
00:34:25,625 --> 00:34:27,958
- [Ta-fu chuckles]
- I suggest you cooperate.

505
00:34:32,041 --> 00:34:33,416
You gave it to me.

506
00:34:34,375 --> 00:34:35,541
Just now.

507
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,125
So, you didn't upload it?

508
00:34:44,833 --> 00:34:47,125
You're a fucking cop. Investigate.

509
00:34:54,916 --> 00:34:57,041
I'm not the only one who wants them dead.

510
00:35:06,041 --> 00:35:07,041
[door opens]

511
00:35:11,083 --> 00:35:12,791
- [bracelet rattling]
- [door closes]

512
00:35:27,708 --> 00:35:29,666
[steady beep]

513
00:35:33,791 --> 00:35:38,291
[rhythmic beeping continues]

514
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:10,666
[Ta-fu grunting]

515
00:36:12,458 --> 00:36:14,416
[no audible dialogue]

516
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:19,250
- [Ta-fu grunting]
- [rapid beeping]

517
00:36:32,458 --> 00:36:35,791
[steady beep]

518
00:36:53,208 --> 00:36:55,416
- [reporter 1] Yeah. Look, I'm not sure.
- [reporter 2] And how much was it?

519
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:56,625
- [reporter 1] The case is coming out.
- [reporter 2] Yes.

520
00:36:56,708 --> 00:36:57,958
- [reporter 3] Hey, the captain!
- [reporter 4] He's here.

521
00:36:58,041 --> 00:36:59,500
[reporter 3] The chief!
The chief is coming!

522
00:37:04,541 --> 00:37:09,083
Ladies and gentlemen of the media.
I'll give you my report.

523
00:37:10,541 --> 00:37:13,208
Through the efforts of our task force,

524
00:37:14,791 --> 00:37:18,666
we've arrested the main suspect
in the serial killing case.

525
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:20,291
Kuo Ta-fu confessed<i>…</i>

526
00:37:20,375 --> 00:37:21,375
WEI MENG-YEN SHOOTING CASE

527
00:37:21,458 --> 00:37:25,208
<i>…</i>that between September 28th
and October 6th,

528
00:37:25,291 --> 00:37:29,833
he committed kidnapping,
murder, assaulting police,

529
00:37:29,916 --> 00:37:31,333
and aiding and abetting murder.

530
00:37:31,416 --> 00:37:32,250
WITCH BABA?

531
00:37:32,333 --> 00:37:33,166
WITCH BABA

532
00:37:33,250 --> 00:37:39,708
This includes the kidnapping of a woman
with the surname Chen on September 28th,

533
00:37:39,791 --> 00:37:43,208
and aiding and abetting the murder
of a man with the surname Wei

534
00:37:43,291 --> 00:37:44,583
on October 1st…

535
00:37:44,666 --> 00:37:45,875
[Wei Yen coughing]

536
00:37:45,958 --> 00:37:49,416
…the drowning of a man
with the surname Liu on October 3rd,

537
00:37:50,375 --> 00:37:53,291
the kidnapping of a man
with the surname Lin on October 4th,

538
00:37:54,458 --> 00:37:59,083
and the fall from a bridge of a man
with the surname Kao on October 5th.

539
00:38:00,833 --> 00:38:02,500
KAO PI - BRAISED EGG

540
00:38:03,375 --> 00:38:07,708
The judicial process has begun,
so many aspects cannot be disclosed.

541
00:38:07,791 --> 00:38:09,291
- Thank you, everyone.
- [reporter 1] Sir, can you--

542
00:38:09,375 --> 00:38:12,458
[reporter 2] A netizen revealed
that Kuo Ta-fu died while being detained.

543
00:38:12,541 --> 00:38:14,041
Any comment on this, sir?

544
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,000
Of course.

545
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:19,541
Kuo Ta-fu committed suicide
while they were in detention.

546
00:38:19,625 --> 00:38:21,541
Did Kuo Ta-fu die
because of Chen Chia-jen?

547
00:38:21,625 --> 00:38:22,916
Definitely not.

548
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:25,833
The main suspect died in your custody.
Shouldn't the police take responsibility?

549
00:38:25,916 --> 00:38:27,708
The judicial process has already begun.

550
00:38:27,791 --> 00:38:29,750
Will the other suspect
also commit suicide and die?

551
00:38:29,833 --> 00:38:32,166
- That's ridiculous.
- Is Wei Yen's life still in danger?

552
00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:33,916
Mr. Wei Meng-yen
is no longer in any danger.

553
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:36,625
[reporter 3] Do you have any idea what
the motive was for Kuo Ta-fu's murders?

554
00:38:36,708 --> 00:38:39,500
As I said, the judicial process
has already begun, so I cannot--

555
00:38:39,583 --> 00:38:41,208
- Will Chen Chia-jen be punished?
- [reporter 4] Sir? Sir?

556
00:38:41,291 --> 00:38:43,875
[reporter 5] Will Kuo Ta-fu's car accident
case continue to be investigated?

557
00:38:43,958 --> 00:38:45,916
The task force
will get to the bottom of it.

558
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,833
- Thank you, everyone.
- [reporters shouting, indistinct]

559
00:38:47,916 --> 00:38:50,541
The judicial process has already begun.
That's all. I'm sorry.

560
00:38:50,625 --> 00:38:51,625
- This way, sir.
- Thank you.

561
00:38:51,708 --> 00:38:53,541
[reporter 1] Sir! Care to comment
on the motive of the crime?

562
00:38:53,625 --> 00:38:56,666
- [reporter 2] One more question! Please!
- [reporter 3] Sir! Do you care to comment?

563
00:39:05,583 --> 00:39:07,500
POLICE OFFICER NUMBER
ENTER PIN

564
00:39:07,583 --> 00:39:08,583
LOG IN

565
00:39:08,666 --> 00:39:10,166
[nasal sigh]

566
00:39:17,916 --> 00:39:23,791
SEARCH CRIMINAL FILES
SEARCH KEYWORD: CHAO KUO-AN

567
00:39:24,250 --> 00:39:27,791
NAME: CHAO KUO-AN

568
00:39:27,875 --> 00:39:30,416
CRIMINAL HISTORY: 2017/7/19 - FRAUD,
2014/3/08 - FRAUD, 2008/6/18 - THEFT

569
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:31,708
CASE AUTHORITY: STANDARD

570
00:39:31,791 --> 00:39:34,833
HIGHLY CONFIDENTIAL

571
00:39:34,916 --> 00:39:37,041
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT
TO CHANGE THE FILE AUTHORITY?

572
00:39:37,125 --> 00:39:38,333
CONFIRM

573
00:39:39,666 --> 00:39:41,041
[Witch Baba's jingle plays]

574
00:39:41,125 --> 00:39:42,916
WITCH BABA

575
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:46,500
[Witch Baba] Hello, guys. I'm Witch Baba.

576
00:39:48,750 --> 00:39:52,583
Even if this serial killing case
seems to be over,

577
00:39:59,291 --> 00:40:01,916
there's actually another killer.

578
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:08,500
Yep. That's right! [giggles]

579
00:40:09,125 --> 00:40:11,916
And one more person will die.

580
00:40:19,750 --> 00:40:22,791
[rapid beeping]

581
00:40:36,625 --> 00:40:39,125
[steady beep]

582
00:40:40,458 --> 00:40:42,500
[closing theme music playing]

583
00:40:42,583 --> 00:40:46,041
[singer singing in Mandarin]

584
00:44:30,833 --> 00:44:35,833
[music ends]
